DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
STOVELL 2018-1231 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 2, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On Certified Order of the District of Columbia Court of Appeals, No. 18-BG-115. Leicester Bryce Stovell, Attorney Registration No. 0038060, last known business address in Washington, District of Columbia, found in contempt for failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before November 13, 2018.
